ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._ExternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._InternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy.ExecuteText : MxBigString (MxCategoryPackageOnly_Lockable) = '----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on deployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Second ExecutionCnt
If Me.01_ObjectDeploy.ExecutionCnt == 2 Then

	IF MyArea._Config.Activate.FB Then
		' Affect Input source
		Me.Object.Script.AffectInputSource = True;
	ENDIF;

	' Add object in Area object
	bfind=False;
	For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
		' Already present
		If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
			bfind = True;
			Exit For;
		Endif;
	Next;
	If Not bfind Then
		For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
			' Already present
			If MyArea.List.Object[i] == "" Then
				MyArea.List.Object[i] = Me.Tagname;
				Exit For;
			Endif;
		Next;	
	Endif;
Endif;

' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectUnDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on undeployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Delete Object from the list
For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
	' Already present
	If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
		MyArea.List.Object[i] = "";
		Exit For;
	Endif;
Next;

CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._ExternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._InternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy.ExecuteText : MxBigString (MxCategoryPackageOnly_Lockable) = '----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on deployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Second ExecutionCnt
If Me.01_ObjectDeploy.ExecutionCnt == 2 Then

	IF MyArea._Config.Activate.FB Then
		' Affect Input source
		Me.Object.Script.AffectInputSource = True;
	ENDIF;

	' Add object in Area object
	bfind=False;
	For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
		' Already present
		If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
			bfind = True;
			Exit For;
		Endif;
	Next;
	If Not bfind Then
		For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
			' Already present
			If MyArea.List.Object[i] == "" Then
				MyArea.List.Object[i] = Me.Tagname;
				Exit For;
			Endif;
		Next;	
	Endif;
Endif;

' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectUnDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on undeployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Delete Object from the list
For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
	' Already present
	If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
		MyArea.List.Object[i] = "";
		Exit For;
	Endif;
Next;

ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._ExternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._InternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy.ExecuteText : MxBigString (MxCategoryPackageOnly_Lockable) = '----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on deployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Second ExecutionCnt
If Me.01_ObjectDeploy.ExecutionCnt == 2 Then

	IF MyArea._Config.Activate.FB Then
		' Affect Input source
		Me.Object.Script.AffectInputSource = True;
	ENDIF;

	' Add object in Area object
	bfind=False;
	For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
		' Already present
		If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
			bfind = True;
			Exit For;
		Endif;
	Next;
	If Not bfind Then
		For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
			' Already present
			If MyArea.List.Object[i] == "" Then
				MyArea.List.Object[i] = Me.Tagname;
				Exit For;
			Endif;
		Next;	
	Endif;
Endif;

' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectUnDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on undeployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Delete Object from the list
For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
	' Already present
	If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
		MyArea.List.Object[i] = "";
		Exit For;
	Endif;
Next;

CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._ExternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._InternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy.ExecuteText : MxBigString (MxCategoryPackageOnly_Lockable) = '----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on deployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Second ExecutionCnt
If Me.01_ObjectDeploy.ExecutionCnt == 2 Then

	IF MyArea._Config.Activate.FB Then
		' Affect Input source
		Me.Object.Script.AffectInputSource = True;
	ENDIF;

	' Add object in Area object
	bfind=False;
	For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
		' Already present
		If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
			bfind = True;
			Exit For;
		Endif;
	Next;
	If Not bfind Then
		For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
			' Already present
			If MyArea.List.Object[i] == "" Then
				MyArea.List.Object[i] = Me.Tagname;
				Exit For;
			Endif;
		Next;	
	Endif;
Endif;

' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectUnDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on undeployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Delete Object from the list
For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
	' Already present
	If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
		MyArea.List.Object[i] = "";
		Exit For;
	Endif;
Next;

ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._ExternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._InternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy.ExecuteText : MxBigString (MxCategoryPackageOnly_Lockable) = '----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on deployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Second ExecutionCnt
If Me.01_ObjectDeploy.ExecutionCnt == 2 Then

	IF MyArea._Config.Activate.FB Then
		' Affect Input source
		Me.Object.Script.AffectInputSource = True;
	ENDIF;

	' Add object in Area object
	bfind=False;
	For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
		' Already present
		If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
			bfind = True;
			Exit For;
		Endif;
	Next;
	If Not bfind Then
		For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
			' Already present
			If MyArea.List.Object[i] == "" Then
				MyArea.List.Object[i] = Me.Tagname;
				Exit For;
			Endif;
		Next;	
	Endif;
Endif;

' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectUnDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on undeployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Delete Object from the list
For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
	' Already present
	If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
		MyArea.List.Object[i] = "";
		Exit For;
	Endif;
Next;

CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._ExternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._InternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy.ExecuteText : MxBigString (MxCategoryPackageOnly_Lockable) = '----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on deployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Second ExecutionCnt
If Me.01_ObjectDeploy.ExecutionCnt == 2 Then

	IF MyArea._Config.Activate.FB Then
		' Affect Input source
		Me.Object.Script.AffectInputSource = True;
	ENDIF;

	' Add object in Area object
	bfind=False;
	For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
		' Already present
		If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
			bfind = True;
			Exit For;
		Endif;
	Next;
	If Not bfind Then
		For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
			' Already present
			If MyArea.List.Object[i] == "" Then
				MyArea.List.Object[i] = Me.Tagname;
				Exit For;
			Endif;
		Next;	
	Endif;
Endif;

' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectUnDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on undeployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Delete Object from the list
For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
	' Already present
	If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
		MyArea.List.Object[i] = "";
		Exit For;
	Endif;
Next;

ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._ExternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._InternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy.ExecuteText : MxBigString (MxCategoryPackageOnly_Lockable) = '----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on deployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Second ExecutionCnt
If Me.01_ObjectDeploy.ExecutionCnt == 2 Then

	IF MyArea._Config.Activate.FB Then
		' Affect Input source
		Me.Object.Script.AffectInputSource = True;
	ENDIF;

	' Add object in Area object
	bfind=False;
	For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
		' Already present
		If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
			bfind = True;
			Exit For;
		Endif;
	Next;
	If Not bfind Then
		For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
			' Already present
			If MyArea.List.Object[i] == "" Then
				MyArea.List.Object[i] = Me.Tagname;
				Exit For;
			Endif;
		Next;	
	Endif;
Endif;

' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectUnDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on undeployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Delete Object from the list
For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
	' Already present
	If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
		MyArea.List.Object[i] = "";
		Exit For;
	Endif;
Next;

CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._ExternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._InternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy.ExecuteText : MxBigString (MxCategoryPackageOnly_Lockable) = '----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on deployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Second ExecutionCnt
If Me.01_ObjectDeploy.ExecutionCnt == 2 Then

	IF MyArea._Config.Activate.FB Then
		' Affect Input source
		Me.Object.Script.AffectInputSource = True;
	ENDIF;

	' Add object in Area object
	bfind=False;
	For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
		' Already present
		If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
			bfind = True;
			Exit For;
		Endif;
	Next;
	If Not bfind Then
		For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
			' Already present
			If MyArea.List.Object[i] == "" Then
				MyArea.List.Object[i] = Me.Tagname;
				Exit For;
			Endif;
		Next;	
	Endif;
Endif;

' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectUnDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on undeployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Delete Object from the list
For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
	' Already present
	If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
		MyArea.List.Object[i] = "";
		Exit For;
	Endif;
Next;

ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._ExternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._InternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy.ExecuteText : MxBigString (MxCategoryPackageOnly_Lockable) = '----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on deployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Second ExecutionCnt
If Me.01_ObjectDeploy.ExecutionCnt == 2 Then

	IF MyArea._Config.Activate.FB Then
		' Affect Input source
		Me.Object.Script.AffectInputSource = True;
	ENDIF;

	' Add object in Area object
	bfind=False;
	For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
		' Already present
		If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
			bfind = True;
			Exit For;
		Endif;
	Next;
	If Not bfind Then
		For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
			' Already present
			If MyArea.List.Object[i] == "" Then
				MyArea.List.Object[i] = Me.Tagname;
				Exit For;
			Endif;
		Next;	
	Endif;
Endif;

' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectUnDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on undeployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Delete Object from the list
For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
	' Already present
	If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
		MyArea.List.Object[i] = "";
		Exit For;
	Endif;
Next;

CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._ExternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._InternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy.ExecuteText : MxBigString (MxCategoryPackageOnly_Lockable) = '----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on deployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Second ExecutionCnt
If Me.01_ObjectDeploy.ExecutionCnt == 2 Then

	IF MyArea._Config.Activate.FB Then
		' Affect Input source
		Me.Object.Script.AffectInputSource = True;
	ENDIF;

	' Add object in Area object
	bfind=False;
	For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
		' Already present
		If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
			bfind = True;
			Exit For;
		Endif;
	Next;
	If Not bfind Then
		For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
			' Already present
			If MyArea.List.Object[i] == "" Then
				MyArea.List.Object[i] = Me.Tagname;
				Exit For;
			Endif;
		Next;	
	Endif;
Endif;

' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectUnDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on undeployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Delete Object from the list
For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
	' Already present
	If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
		MyArea.List.Object[i] = "";
		Exit For;
	Endif;
Next;

ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._ExternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._InternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy.ExecuteText : MxBigString (MxCategoryPackageOnly_Lockable) = '----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on deployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Second ExecutionCnt
If Me.01_ObjectDeploy.ExecutionCnt == 2 Then

	IF MyArea._Config.Activate.FB Then
		' Affect Input source
		Me.Object.Script.AffectInputSource = True;
	ENDIF;

	' Add object in Area object
	bfind=False;
	For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
		' Already present
		If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
			bfind = True;
			Exit For;
		Endif;
	Next;
	If Not bfind Then
		For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
			' Already present
			If MyArea.List.Object[i] == "" Then
				MyArea.List.Object[i] = Me.Tagname;
				Exit For;
			Endif;
		Next;	
	Endif;
Endif;

' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectUnDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on undeployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Delete Object from the list
For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
	' Already present
	If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
		MyArea.List.Object[i] = "";
		Exit For;
	Endif;
Next;

CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._ExternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._InternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy.ExecuteText : MxBigString (MxCategoryPackageOnly_Lockable) = '----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on deployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Second ExecutionCnt
If Me.01_ObjectDeploy.ExecutionCnt == 2 Then

	IF MyArea._Config.Activate.FB Then
		' Affect Input source
		Me.Object.Script.AffectInputSource = True;
	ENDIF;

	' Add object in Area object
	bfind=False;
	For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
		' Already present
		If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
			bfind = True;
			Exit For;
		Endif;
	Next;
	If Not bfind Then
		For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
			' Already present
			If MyArea.List.Object[i] == "" Then
				MyArea.List.Object[i] = Me.Tagname;
				Exit For;
			Endif;
		Next;	
	Endif;
Endif;

' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectUnDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on undeployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Delete Object from the list
For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
	' Already present
	If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
		MyArea.List.Object[i] = "";
		Exit For;
	Endif;
Next;

ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._ExternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._InternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy.ExecuteText : MxBigString (MxCategoryPackageOnly_Lockable) = '----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on deployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Second ExecutionCnt
If Me.01_ObjectDeploy.ExecutionCnt == 2 Then

	IF MyArea._Config.Activate.FB Then
		' Affect Input source
		Me.Object.Script.AffectInputSource = True;
	ENDIF;

	' Add object in Area object
	bfind=False;
	For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
		' Already present
		If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
			bfind = True;
			Exit For;
		Endif;
	Next;
	If Not bfind Then
		For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
			' Already present
			If MyArea.List.Object[i] == "" Then
				MyArea.List.Object[i] = Me.Tagname;
				Exit For;
			Endif;
		Next;	
	Endif;
Endif;

' Script Name : ObjectUnDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on undeployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Delete Object from the list
For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
	' Already present
	If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
		MyArea.List.Object[i] = "";
		Exit For;
	Endif;
Next;

CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._ExternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._InternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy.ExecuteText : MxBigString (MxCategoryPackageOnly_Lockable) = '----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on deployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Second ExecutionCnt
If Me.01_ObjectDeploy.ExecutionCnt == 2 Then

	IF MyArea._Config.Activate.FB Then
		' Affect Input source
		Me.Object.Script.AffectInputSource = True;
	ENDIF;

	' Add object in Area object
	bfind=False;
	For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
		' Already present
		If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
			bfind = True;
			Exit For;
		Endif;
	Next;
	If Not bfind Then
		For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
			' Already present
			If MyArea.List.Object[i] == "" Then
				MyArea.List.Object[i] = Me.Tagname;
				Exit For;
			Endif;
		Next;	
	Endif;
Endif;

'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Delete Object from the list

	' Already present
	If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
		MyArea.List.Object[i] = "";
		Exit For;
	Endif;
Next;

ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._ExternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._InternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy.ExecuteText : MxBigString (MxCategoryPackageOnly_Lockable) = '----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on deployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Second ExecutionCnt
If Me.01_ObjectDeploy.ExecutionCnt == 2 Then

	IF MyArea._Config.Activate.FB Then
		' Affect Input source
		Me.Object.Script.AffectInputSource = True;
	ENDIF;

	' Add object in Area object
	bfind=False;
	For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
		' Already present
		If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
			bfind = True;
			Exit For;
		Endif;
	Next;
	If Not bfind Then
		For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
			' Already present
			If MyArea.List.Object[i] == "" Then
				MyArea.List.Object[i] = Me.Tagname;
				Exit For;
			Endif;
		Next;	
	Endif;
Endif;

	Endif;
Next;

CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._ExternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._InternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy.ExecuteText : MxBigString (MxCategoryPackageOnly_Lockable) = '----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on deployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Second ExecutionCnt
If Me.01_ObjectDeploy.ExecutionCnt == 2 Then

	IF MyArea._Config.Activate.FB Then
		' Affect Input source
		Me.Object.Script.AffectInputSource = True;
	ENDIF;

	' Add object in Area object
	bfind=False;
	For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
		' Already present
		If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
			bfind = True;
			Exit For;
		Endif;
	Next;
	If Not bfind Then
		For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
			' Already present
			If MyArea.List.Object[i] == "" Then
				MyArea.List.Object[i] = Me.Tagname;
				Exit For;
			Endif;
		Next;	
	Endif;
Endif;

CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 05_AffectInputSource.ExecuteText : MxBigString (MxCategoryPackageOnly_Lockable) = '----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : AffectInputSource
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script to affect input source
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Reset Trigger
Me.Object.Script.AffectInputSource=False;

' Affect Inputsource
Me.PV.Input.InputSource = "Me.PV_FB";
CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 05_AffectInputSource._Binary : MxQualifiedStruct (MxCategoryWriteable_C_Lockable) = 0
CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 05_AffectInputSource.AliasReferences : MxReferenceType (MxCategoryWriteable_C_Lockable) = No Data
CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 05_AffectInputSource.Aliases : MxString (MxCategoryPackageOnly_Lockable) = No Data
CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 05_AffectInputSource._TriggerTypeEnum : MxString (MxCategory_Constant) = WhileTrue,WhileFalse,OnTrue,OnFalse,DataChange,Periodic

		Exit For;
	Endif;
Next;

ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._ExternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._InternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy.ExecuteText : MxBigString (MxCategoryPackageOnly_Lockable) = '----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on deployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Second ExecutionCnt
If Me.01_ObjectDeploy.ExecutionCnt == 2 Then

	IF MyArea._Config.Activate.FB Then
		' Affect Input source
		Me.Object.Script.AffectInputSource = True;
	ENDIF;

	' Add object in Area object
	bfind=False;
	For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
		' Already present
		If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
			bfind = True;
			Exit For;
		Endif;
	Next;
	If Not bfind Then
		For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
			' Already present
			If MyArea.List.Object[i] == "" Then
				MyArea.List.Object[i] = Me.Tagname;
				Exit For;
			Endif;
		Next;	
	Endif;
Endif;

	' Already present
	If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then

		Exit For;
	Endif;
Next;

CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._ExternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._InternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy.ExecuteText : MxBigString (MxCategoryPackageOnly_Lockable) = '----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on deployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Second ExecutionCnt
If Me.01_ObjectDeploy.ExecutionCnt == 2 Then

	IF MyArea._Config.Activate.FB Then
		' Affect Input source
		Me.Object.Script.AffectInputSource = True;
	ENDIF;

	' Add object in Area object
	bfind=False;
	For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
		' Already present
		If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
			bfind = True;
			Exit For;
		Endif;
	Next;
	If Not bfind Then
		For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
			' Already present
			If MyArea.List.Object[i] == "" Then
				MyArea.List.Object[i] = Me.Tagname;
				Exit For;
			Endif;
		Next;	
	Endif;
Endif;

' Script Name : ObjectUnDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on undeployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Delete Object from the list
For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
	' Already present
	If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
		MyArea.List.Object[i] = "";
		Exit For;
	Endif;
Next;

ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._ExternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._InternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy.ExecuteText : MxBigString (MxCategoryPackageOnly_Lockable) = '----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on deployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Second ExecutionCnt
If Me.01_ObjectDeploy.ExecutionCnt == 2 Then

	IF MyArea._Config.Activate.FB Then
		' Affect Input source
		Me.Object.Script.AffectInputSource = True;
	ENDIF;

	' Add object in Area object
	bfind=False;
	For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
		' Already present
		If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
			bfind = True;
			Exit For;
		Endif;
	Next;
	If Not bfind Then
		For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
			' Already present
			If MyArea.List.Object[i] == "" Then
				MyArea.List.Object[i] = Me.Tagname;
				Exit For;
			Endif;
		Next;	
	Endif;
Endif;

' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectUnDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on undeployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Delete Object from the list
For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
	' Already present
	If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
		MyArea.List.Object[i] = "";
		Exit For;
	Endif;
Next;

CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._ExternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._InternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy.ExecuteText : MxBigString (MxCategoryPackageOnly_Lockable) = '----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on deployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Second ExecutionCnt
If Me.01_ObjectDeploy.ExecutionCnt == 2 Then

	IF MyArea._Config.Activate.FB Then
		' Affect Input source
		Me.Object.Script.AffectInputSource = True;
	ENDIF;

	' Add object in Area object
	bfind=False;
	For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
		' Already present
		If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
			bfind = True;
			Exit For;
		Endif;
	Next;
	If Not bfind Then
		For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
			' Already present
			If MyArea.List.Object[i] == "" Then
				MyArea.List.Object[i] = Me.Tagname;
				Exit For;
			Endif;
		Next;	
	Endif;
Endif;

' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectUnDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on undeployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Delete Object from the list
For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
	' Already present
	If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
		MyArea.List.Object[i] = "";
		Exit For;
	Endif;
Next;

ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._ExternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._InternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy.ExecuteText : MxBigString (MxCategoryPackageOnly_Lockable) = '----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on deployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Second ExecutionCnt
If Me.01_ObjectDeploy.ExecutionCnt == 2 Then

	IF MyArea._Config.Activate.FB Then
		' Affect Input source
		Me.Object.Script.AffectInputSource = True;
	ENDIF;

	' Add object in Area object
	bfind=False;
	For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
		' Already present
		If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
			bfind = True;
			Exit For;
		Endif;
	Next;
	If Not bfind Then
		For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
			' Already present
			If MyArea.List.Object[i] == "" Then
				MyArea.List.Object[i] = Me.Tagname;
				Exit For;
			Endif;
		Next;	
	Endif;
Endif;

' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectUnDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on undeployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Delete Object from the list
For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
	' Already present
	If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
		MyArea.List.Object[i] = "";
		Exit For;
	Endif;
Next;

CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._ExternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._InternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy.ExecuteText : MxBigString (MxCategoryPackageOnly_Lockable) = '----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on deployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Second ExecutionCnt
If Me.01_ObjectDeploy.ExecutionCnt == 2 Then

	IF MyArea._Config.Activate.FB Then
		' Affect Input source
		Me.Object.Script.AffectInputSource = True;
	ENDIF;

	' Add object in Area object
	bfind=False;
	For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
		' Already present
		If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
			bfind = True;
			Exit For;
		Endif;
	Next;
	If Not bfind Then
		For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
			' Already present
			If MyArea.List.Object[i] == "" Then
				MyArea.List.Object[i] = Me.Tagname;
				Exit For;
			Endif;
		Next;	
	Endif;
Endif;

' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectUnDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on undeployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Delete Object from the list
For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
	' Already present
	If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
		MyArea.List.Object[i] = "";
		Exit For;
	Endif;
Next;

ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._ExternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._InternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy.ExecuteText : MxBigString (MxCategoryPackageOnly_Lockable) = '----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on deployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Second ExecutionCnt
If Me.01_ObjectDeploy.ExecutionCnt == 2 Then

	IF MyArea._Config.Activate.FB Then
		' Affect Input source
		Me.Object.Script.AffectInputSource = True;
	ENDIF;

	' Add object in Area object
	bfind=False;
	For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
		' Already present
		If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
			bfind = True;
			Exit For;
		Endif;
	Next;
	If Not bfind Then
		For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
			' Already present
			If MyArea.List.Object[i] == "" Then
				MyArea.List.Object[i] = Me.Tagname;
				Exit For;
			Endif;
		Next;	
	Endif;
Endif;

' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectUnDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on undeployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Delete Object from the list
For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
	' Already present
	If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
		MyArea.List.Object[i] = "";
		Exit For;
	Endif;
Next;

CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._ExternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._InternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy.ExecuteText : MxBigString (MxCategoryPackageOnly_Lockable) = '----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on deployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Second ExecutionCnt
If Me.01_ObjectDeploy.ExecutionCnt == 2 Then

	IF MyArea._Config.Activate.FB Then
		' Affect Input source
		Me.Object.Script.AffectInputSource = True;
	ENDIF;

	' Add object in Area object
	bfind=False;
	For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
		' Already present
		If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
			bfind = True;
			Exit For;
		Endif;
	Next;
	If Not bfind Then
		For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
			' Already present
			If MyArea.List.Object[i] == "" Then
				MyArea.List.Object[i] = Me.Tagname;
				Exit For;
			Endif;
		Next;	
	Endif;
Endif;

' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectUnDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on undeployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Delete Object from the list
For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
	' Already present
	If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
		MyArea.List.Object[i] = "";
		Exit For;
	Endif;
Next;

ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._ExternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._InternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy.ExecuteText : MxBigString (MxCategoryPackageOnly_Lockable) = '----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on deployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Second ExecutionCnt
If Me.01_ObjectDeploy.ExecutionCnt == 2 Then

	IF MyArea._Config.Activate.FB Then
		' Affect Input source
		Me.Object.Script.AffectInputSource = True;
	ENDIF;

	' Add object in Area object
	bfind=False;
	For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
		' Already present
		If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
			bfind = True;
			Exit For;
		Endif;
	Next;
	If Not bfind Then
		For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
			' Already present
			If MyArea.List.Object[i] == "" Then
				MyArea.List.Object[i] = Me.Tagname;
				Exit For;
			Endif;
		Next;	
	Endif;
Endif;

' Script Name : ObjectUnDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on undeployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Delete Object from the list
For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
	' Already present
	If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
		MyArea.List.Object[i] = "";
		Exit For;
	Endif;
Next;

CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._ExternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._InternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
CONFIGURABLEATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy.ExecuteText : MxBigString (MxCategoryPackageOnly_Lockable) = '----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on deployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Second ExecutionCnt
If Me.01_ObjectDeploy.ExecutionCnt == 2 Then

	IF MyArea._Config.Activate.FB Then
		' Affect Input source
		Me.Object.Script.AffectInputSource = True;
	ENDIF;

	' Add object in Area object
	bfind=False;
	For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
		' Already present
		If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
			bfind = True;
			Exit For;
		Endif;
	Next;
	If Not bfind Then
		For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
			' Already present
			If MyArea.List.Object[i] == "" Then
				MyArea.List.Object[i] = Me.Tagname;
				Exit For;
			Endif;
		Next;	
	Endif;
Endif;

' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectUnDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on undeployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Delete Object from the list
For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
	' Already present
	If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
		MyArea.List.Object[i] = "";
		Exit For;
	Endif;
Next;

ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._ExternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy._InternalName : MxString (MxCategory_SystemInternal) = No Data
ATTRIBUTE 01_ObjectDeploy.ExecuteText : MxBigString (MxCategoryPackageOnly_Lockable) = '----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on deployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Second ExecutionCnt
If Me.01_ObjectDeploy.ExecutionCnt == 2 Then

	IF MyArea._Config.Activate.FB Then
		' Affect Input source
		Me.Object.Script.AffectInputSource = True;
	ENDIF;

	' Add object in Area object
	bfind=False;
	For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
		' Already present
		If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
			bfind = True;
			Exit For;
		Endif;
	Next;
	If Not bfind Then
		For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
			' Already present
			If MyArea.List.Object[i] == "" Then
				MyArea.List.Object[i] = Me.Tagname;
				Exit For;
			Endif;
		Next;	
	Endif;
Endif;

' Object Name : $dwGenAnalogIn
' Script Name : ObjectUnDeploy
'---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
'
' Description : Script execute on undeployement
'
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Creator : LDE
' Date : 01/08/2008
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

' Declaration
Dim i		as integer;
Dim bfind 	as boolean;

' Delete Object from the list
For i=1 To MyArea.List.Object.dimension1 
	' Already present
	If MyArea.List.Object[i] == Me.Tagname Then
		MyArea.List.Object[i] = "";
		Exit For;
	Endif;
Next;
